title: Rabbit Foundation Holiday Party
desc: Annual Holiday Party and Fundraiser for Los Angeles Rabbit Foundation, a non profit 501(c)3 organization dedicated to helping abandoned domestic rabbits.  ? Enjoy an evening of fun?with others who care about abandoned rabbits! ? FAQs ? Are there ID requirements or an age limit to enter the event? Wine and beer will only be served to those over 21, so if you plan to enjoy a beverage, please bring your ID.? ? What are my transport/parking options getting to the event? There is parking on two levels at the Center. If the parking lot is full, you can park on Temescal Canyon and take a staircase up to the event. If you need assistance with parking, please let us know. What can/can't I bring to the event? Please leave your companion animals safe at home. Where can I contact the organizer with any questions? You can contact the organizer at  losangelesrabbits@gmail.com . ? Is my registration/ticket transferrable? Yes, but it is non-refundable. Dress code?  Holiday party attire?(dressy but not black tie). Dress comfortably and enjoy yourselves!
